@NODE Intro "Introduction"

@{b}Noughts And Crosses Deluxe v1.0@{ub}

Noughts And Crosses Deluxe is an intelligent noughts and crosses game for the Amiga.

@ENDNODE

@NODE Install "Installation"
@NEXT Params

Noughts And Crosses Deluxe requires the font mFast to be present.

Clicking the button below will install this font.

Click @{"here" LINK "Inst2"} for more info.
Click @{"here" SYSTEM "installer NoughtsAndCrosses.install APPNAME NoughtsAndCrossesDeluxe MINUSER Expert"} to install.

@{i}Note for users of Cachefont:
Remember to run Makefontlist once the new font has been installed.>{ui}

@ENDNODE

@NODE Inst2 "Details of installation"

The install process will carry out the following steps.

1. Will copy the font mFast to your FONTS: directory

@ENDNODE

@NODE Spec "Requirements"

@{b}Hardware@{ub}
This @{i}should@{ui} run on any Amiga with WB2.0 or above (although it has only been tested on WB3.0).

@{b}Software@{ub}
Requires the font @{FG SHINE}mFast (size 28)@{FG TEXT} to be present in FONTS:

This font is included in the archive and will be automatically copied by the installer.

Also requires AMOS.Library (not included), but most people have this already.

@ENDNODE

